      "text": "Teeñu falaffija to ikrihtu/ weenê/ zik tas warreja apehſt/ tad ta Saule eekahrfe/ tad tas uſſe."
    },
    {
      "n": 22,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un feftã Deena falaffija tee rnteek Maisês/ diwi Some- preekſch weena/ un wiſſi iſeet."
    },
    {
      "n": 23,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "wiſſes Wirfneeki nahze/ un izzija to Mohſum."
    },
    {
      "n": 3,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un wiꞥſch fazztja uſteem: irr tas/ ko tas KUNGS unnajs/ riht irr ta KUN- Duffſchana/ ta Swehta ſefchanas Deena ta KUN- ko juhszept gribbat/ to zep- un ko juhs gribbat wahriht/ ahrajt/ un wiſſu/ kas atleeſ abbajeet/ ka tas lihds Nih- tohp furgahts."
    },
    {
      "n": 4,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un tee glabbaja to lihds am/ itt ka Mohſus bij pa- iſ/ un tas ne ſmirdeja/ ir ps reekſch ta ne bija."
    },
    {
      "n": 5,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Tad fazzija Mohſus: Eh- chodeen/ jo chodeen irr ta GA Duffſchanas Deena/ en juhs Laukã neneeka ne eet."
    },
    {
      "n": 6,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Seſchas Deenas buhs falaffiht/ bet ſeptita Dee- ta Duffſchanas Deena/ tas ne buhs."
    },
    {
      "n": 7,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Tatſchu ſeptitã Deenã zi- teein Laudim iſgahje/ ka tee tu/ un ne atradde neneeka."
    },
    {
      "n": 8,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Tad fazzija tas KUNGS ohſu: Zik ilgi juhs leedsatees"
    },
    {
      "n": 29,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Redſeet/ tadeht ka tas KUNGS juns to Duffſcha- nas Deenn dewisirr/ tapehz dohd wiꞥſch juns ſeftã Deenã diwejo Deenu Maisi/ lai ikweens fauã Weeta paleek/ un lai ne weens no fawas Weetas ſeptitã Deenã"
    },
    {
      "n": 30,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Ta duſſeja tee Eaudis ſep- titã Deenã."
    },
    {
      "n": 31,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un Israëta Namã fauze winna Wahrdũ Mann/ un tas bija itt ka Korianađra Sehla bal- ta un winna Smaſſa bija/ itt ka Karraschas ar Meddu."
    },
    {
      "n": 32,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Wehl fazzija Mohſus: ſchis irr tas Wahrdũ/ ko tas KUNGS irr pawehlejs/ piſdajt kahdu Gomeru no ta par Glab- baschanu preekſch juhſeem Behr- nu Behrnceim/ ka tee redſeht warr to Maisi/ ko es juns etmu ehſt dewis Tuſſneſi/ kad es juhs iſ- weddu no Eqiptes Semines."
    },
    {
      "n": 33,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un Mohſus fazztja uſ Aarõnu: nemm weenu Kaſfu/ un leeſ eekſch ta weenu pillu Go- mern no ta Mann/ un noleez to preekſch ta KUNGA Waiga par Glabbaſchanu preekſch juhſeem Behrnu Behrneem."
    },
    {
      "n": 34,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Ittin ka kas KUNGS Mohſum bij pawehlejs ta noſik- ke to Aarons klaht pee tahs Lee- zibaſ par Sargaschanu."
    },
    {
      "n": 35,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un Israëta Behrni ehDe to Mann tschetrdesmits Gad- dus kamehr tee mahjojamãSem- S mê"
    }
